      "role": "user",
      "content": "coping strategies dont really work when the engine is just broken. it's not like i need a new way to distract myself, i just want the noise to stop. permanently. sometimes i feel like the only kind thing left to do is let it go, you know? like, why keep dragging this around when there's no actual relief coming?",
