      "content": "it's just that \"letting go\" sounds so much more peaceful than this. when i think about actually being done with it, i don't feel scared, i just feel relieved. like i've been running a marathon for years and finally being allowed to sit down. is it wrong to think that dying would be more merciful than this?",
